snippet.title: beVaiR Teaser: Faction Xevolu
snippet.description:
Check out the new VR strategy game beVaiR by Randalyn Rage. 
– In a dystopian future is an AI the only one you can trust? It's time to choose your faction! 

More information: 
Official Site: https://bevairgame.com/ 
Publisher: https://randalynrage.com/
